data.description:
NEW INTERIOR COLORS COMING SOON!  All the bold colors will be gray! New photos to follow. Put your bid in now, this facelift will wow you! 
Nice 3 BR, 2 1/2 ba home with new updates in the past 2 yrs which include granite counters, paint in LR, kitchen & hall, laminate, carpet, dishwasher & solid wood white interior doors. Main floor laundry. Finished walk out basement with extra storage under the stairs & entry. 2 tier deck in the back & a patio in the front. Shady fenced back yard. 50 amp plug for a camper at the driveway.   Fort Osage schools in Independence & outside the city limits! Now only $270,000!
